data.description: 2705 Sqft Ranch Style 3 bedroom, 3.5 Bathroom Home! Property features: beautiful sliding barn doors that add a touch of rustic charm, open living room and dining area with new flooring, family room with cozy fireplace, updated kitchen with granite countertops, pantry, buffet area, and tankless water heaters that are great for large families. Relax after a long day in the freestanding bathtub or walk-in shower in the oversized primary suite, designed with your comfort in mind. The additional bedrooms all have ensuite bathrooms and spacious closets. The laundry room with sink, storage, and folding table makes laundry day a breeze. This property also has a double attached garage, workshop, concrete patio, and a huge backyard! Must See!
